            {
                "comment": "John is a very caring professor and you get the impression that he cares about your progress. The class is divided into three \"portfolios,\" with a few other assignments that sometimes feel like busy work. Overall, Professor Mulvihill gives great feedback and is a fun lecturer and I would highly recommend it to anyone who must take English 100. ",
                "difficulty_rating": 2,
                "quality_rating": 5
            },
            {
